{"id":534436,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/07/【立此存照】天津警方：删评论是怕喷子污了大家/","date":"2016-07-08T03:39:58Z","modified":"2016-07-08T03:56:01Z","title":"【立此存照】天津警方：删评论是怕喷子污了大家的眼","content":"<p>@平安天津于中国时间2016年7月7日发表了关于赵威的“情况通报”，迅速引来大量评论。数字时代编辑截取以下图片时，该条微博尚有1089条评论：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_534437\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-534437\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津1.png\" alt=\"平安天津1\" width=\"500\" height=\"648\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津1.png 1806w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津1-231x300.png 231w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津1-768x996.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津1-790x1024.png 790w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@平安天津 微博截图一</span></p></div>\n<p>若干小时后，评论只剩下21条：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_534438\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-534438\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津2.jpg\" alt=\"平安天津2\" width=\"500\" height=\"676\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津2.jpg 1567w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津2-222x300.jpg 222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津2-768x1039.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津2-757x1024.jpg 757w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@平安天津 微博截图二</span></p></div>\n<p><strong><br />\n天津警方并公开回应网民质疑，称删除微博评论是“怕那些喷子污了大家的眼”：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_534439\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-534439\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津3.jpg\" alt=\"平安天津3\" width=\"550\" height=\"157\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津3.jpg 1771w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津3-300x85.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津3-768x219.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/平安天津3-1024x291.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@平安天津 微博回复 截图</span></p></div>\n<p>（在大陆网络语境中，“喷子”一般被“爱国人士”用来指对政府不满、不认同官方口径的网民。）</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[22646,17389,8616,9212]}